text: Atsuyarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Sukkulovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 118 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Dyurtyuli, 4 km from Sukkulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Atsuyarovo
